'''Mor''' or '''Moor''' is a [[tonal language|tonal]] [[Austronesian language]] in the putative [[Cenderawasih languages|Cenderawasih]] (Geelvink Bay) of [[Indonesian Papua]]. It is not closely related to other languages.
